  "description": "Sher Dhan Rai (born 25 June 1970) is a Nepalese politician who served as the first Chief Minister of Koshi Province from February 2018 to August 2021. A member of the CPN (UML), he has held several key positions, including Minister of Information and Communications in the first Oli cabinet. Rai has been elected to various parliamentary bodies, such as the 2nd Nepalese Constituent Assembly and the Provincial Assembly of Province No. 1.",
